product.title: ASUS Vivobook 15 Intel Core i3 11th Gen (15.6 inch, 8GB, 512GB, Windows 11 Home, MS Office 2021, Intel UHD, Full HD IPS Display, Grey, X515EA-EZ311WS)
product.description:
Streamlined Computing Tasks

Boost your efficiency with the ASUS Vivobook 15 X515EA-EZ311WS Windows Laptop, which features a 3GHz Intel Core i3-1115G4 11th Gen processor that delivers rapid and responsive computing. Furthermore, with a rapid refresh rate of up to 60Hz, this laptop makes sure that fast-paced content and games are rendered with precision and minimal motion distortion.


Striking Visual Experience

Flaunting a 15.6-inch IPS screen, this laptop creates a visually engaging and productive environment to elevate your work and entertainment experience. What’s more, with a refresh rate of up to 60Hz, this laptop ensures a captivating viewing experience, free from the disruption of motion blur during action scenes.


Cortana Support

Integrating Cortana Support technology, this 15.6-inch laptop promises a dynamic and full-bodied sound experience. As a result, you can engross yourself in the ultimate gaming experience, feel the intensity of every precise move, and capture the subtleties of virtual environments.


Intel UHD Graphics Card

The Intel UHD graphics card delivers high-quality graphics rendering, making it ideal for graphic design and content creation.


512GB M.2 PCIe NVMe SSD

With a substantial 512GB M.2 PCIe NVMe SSD, this laptop is designed for prompt data retrieval, leading to reduced loading times and quick boot times.


Clear Webcam

Facilitate high-definition video communication with its webcam, which delivers sharp and detailed visuals. Additionally, its built-in ensures that your voice is captured with clarity.


Windows 11 Home Operating System

Running on the Windows 11 Home operating system, this laptop offers a hassle-free and efficient user experience, making it suitable for various computing needs.


Dependable Battery Performance

Running on a substantial 37Wh lithium-ion battery, this laptop has an extended battery life of up to 4 hours, enabling you to stay connected and productive throughout the day without the worry of running out of power.


Flexible Connectivity Options

Built with a USB 3.2 port a USB 3.2 Type-C, two USB 2.0 ports, an HDMI 1.4 port, a 3.5mm AUX, and one MicroSD Card Reader, this ASUS laptop provides hassle-free connectivity, allowing you to connect peripherals and accessories effortlessly. Additionally, stay connected with ease as this laptop's IEEE 802.11a/b/g/n/ac ensures seamless internet access.


Touch to Login

Unlocking this laptop is super easy and safe as its touchpad has a fingerprint sensor, and with Windows Hello, you don't have to Type your password but just touch it once.


Lightweight Design

With an overall weight of just 1.8 kg, this laptop is lightweight and helps keeps up with your fast-paced lifestyle.
